  "body": "**Spec:**\r\n- [x] Pass consensus spec v1.1.9 spec tests\r\n- [x] Pass consensus spec v1.1.10 spec tests #10298\r\n- [x] Pass bellatrix forkchoice spec tests #forkchoice #10284\r\n- [x] Rename receipt_root -> receipts_root\r\n- [x] Rename execute_payload -> notify_new_payload\r\n\r\n**Engine API:**\r\n- [x] Support authentication for engine API #10236\r\n- [x] Use `engine_exchangeTransitionConfigurationV1` to check EL config\r\n- [x] Handle nil cases and`payloadStatus` invalid in respond\r\n- [x] Unify --execution-provider and --http-web3provider\r\n- [x] Better status, error and nil handling for responses\r\n- [x] Update to kiln v2\r\n - [x] Review endianess conversations. More places are doing this wrong\r\n - [x] Call fcu as part of processing attestations and updating head\r\n - [x] Log out time taken for calls to the execution node in the critical paths.\r\n - [x] Add in tracing for execution node calls.\r\n\r\n**Optimistic sync:**\r\n- [x] Can optimistically sync beacon node under various scenarios \r\n- [x] Validator assignments are blocked under optimistic mode #10200\r\n- [x] Can remove invalid `SYNCING/ACCEPTED` blocks\r\n- [ ] Beacon APIs can properly respond under optimistic mode\r\n- [x] Optimistically import any post-merge block https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2844\r\n- [x] P2p scorer and gossip pub beacon block under optimistic mode #10274\r\n- [x] Beacon block sync validation under optimistic mode #10233\r\n- [x] Sync service should still pass block with optimistic parent to blockchain service\r\n- [ ] Retrospective transition block checking\r\n- [x] Ensuring sync gracefully handles an offline EE (gracefully handle offline EE w/o penalizing innocent peers or wasting resources). Pause sync when execution layer is offline?\r\n- [ ] #10487\r\n\r\n**Web3signer**\r\n- [x] add BLOCK_V3 mapping for web3signer refer to tracking issue #10053 \r\n- [x] update Web3Signer binary for web3signer\r\n- [x] remove condition check in e2e that stops tests right before Bellatrix\r\n\r\n**Code health:**\r\n- [x] Clean up process block with optimistic sync\r\n- [ ] Cache eth1 hash and total difficulty for validator finding terminal transition block\r\n- [ ] Set a max allowance for looking back to find terminal transition block\r\n- [ ] Context timeout doesn't fail validator duty\r\n\r\n**UX:**\r\n- [x] Add `--kiln-testnet` flag\r\n- [ ] Complete fee recipient tasks #10292\r\n- [x] Check for terminal block during proposer preparation #10497 \r\n- [x] Don't call fcu update twice to propose block #10481 \r\n- [ ] Investiate why payload ID cache hit/miss ratio is not 100%\r\n- [x] Improve logging. \r\n    - [x] Identify beacon block with non empty payload\r\n    - [ ] Estimate time to TTD and log it\r\n    - [ ] What else?\r\n\r\n**Testing:**\r\n- [ ] Support e2e test pass Bellatrix epoch and reach ttd\r\n- [ ] Differential fuzz engine API req/res\r\n- [ ] Test generator Bellatrix version block\r\n- [x] Transaction Generator for execution nodes.\r\n- [ ] Configurable tool to trigger optimistic sync.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Eth2 API**\r\n- [x] Update all the Bellatrix related beacon endpoints\r\n- [x] Update all the Bellatrix related validator endpoints\r\n- [x] Update all the Bellatrix related debug endpoints\r\n- [x] Add `is_optimistic` field to all relevant endpoints \r\n\r\n**Prysm API**\r\n- [x] Update all the Bellatrix related beacon endpoints\r\n\r\n**Bugs**\r\n- [ ] Beacon block's eth1 data hash is 0s\r\n- [x] TTD checks are being bypassed in e2e\r\n- [x] If the execution engine has a restart, prysm stalls and does nothing.\r\n\r\n**Final:**\r\n- [x] Cont merging `kiln` to `develop` (mostly go.mod changes)\r\n\r\nKiln spec: https://hackmd.io/@n0ble/kiln-spec\r\nMilestones tracker: https://notes.ethereum.org/@timbeiko/kiln-milestones\r\nEngine API test vectors: https://notes.ethereum.org/rmVErCfCRPKGqGkUe89-Kg?view\r\n",
